<br>
 Unfortunately, this quest is also a mangy dog like the kobolds itself. Turning in the scroll case netted me 5plat. I was dumbfounded... check my inventory and realise I had no open slots. Feeling incredibly stupid, and more than a little burnt, I loaded and converted another case with the volumes of spare scrolls I had, checked my inventory and handed it in again. Reward was 31plat. Either this is doable for a main reward once... or it flat out blows. I suspect the latter.<br>
<br>
 If another out there is currently doing this quest, please complete it. I may have botched my chance...<br>
<br>
